folder: Sands Street & Gold Street, Brooklyn, NY
text:
194-198 Sands Street, south side, between Gold Street and Hudson Ave., from the head of Green Lane, showing two views of an old frame house sandwiched between modern dwellings.
June 26, 1934.
View 2: April 4, 1938.
P. L. Sperr.

folder: Sands Street & Gold Street, Brooklyn, NY
text:
